WEBVTT

00:03:58.910 --> 00:04:00.688
someone else wrote: "Same thing here.

00:04:00.712 --> 00:04:03.785
I actually got a natural high
and a good mood for the entire day,

00:04:03.809 --> 00:04:08.237
since I remember seeing
all of this matrix text in class,

00:04:08.261 --> 00:04:10.976
and here I'm all like, 'I know kung fu.'"

00:04:11.000 --> 00:04:15.261
(Laughter)

00:04:15.285 --> 00:04:17.636
We get a lot of feedback
along those lines.

00:04:17.660 --> 00:04:19.341
This clearly was helping people.

00:04:19.365 --> 00:04:23.067
